6. Dollar Amounts

Dogecoin is not AMC, Dogecoin is not GameStop.

While I can see the comparison of the little guy versus the big guy, What is happening on Wall Street and what is happening in the crypto market are totally different. The only thing that they share are charts

5. Proof

There's a lot of things that people are saying Dogecoin can or Dogecoin will be.

Be like the Dogecoin blockchain and don't trust anything until it's verified.

Spreading hype will always be worse then people who are spreading fear uncertainty and doubt

4. Hate

Hating on another project is not #DoOnlyGoodEveryday 

I do think that there are some projects out there that are not good. However it wasn't that long ago that people were saying the exact same thing about Dogecoin / still are

Research a project and give suggestions

3. Influencers

Anyone who's making memes, adding code, or talking about Dogecoin is part of the Dogecoin project in my heart.

But I've been seeing a lot of people who are just adding selfies of themselves with nothing dogecoin related to the Dogecoin hashtag. That's not good.

Okay I have a bunch of things to get off my chest about the current Dogecoin Community. 

Next week I am planning on doing a lot of things Dogecoin related put I will admit these things have been making me less interested in doing them. But I know there are amazing people.
